00:12:39.540 --> 00:12:44.070
It's a fight that has been
raw and rowdy, and often very,

00:12:44.070 --> 00:12:46.470
very partisan from the beginning.

00:12:46.470 --> 00:12:51.400
And just as we might see
now, throughout history

00:12:51.400 --> 00:12:54.850
as many Americans have demanded
their place at the table

00:12:54.850 --> 00:12:57.490
and have claimed their
voice in our democracy,

00:12:57.490 --> 00:13:01.300
many others have fought
just as hard to stop them,

00:13:01.300 --> 00:13:04.840
to restrict that right to vote.

00:13:04.840 --> 00:13:08.370
And so that is ultimately
