00:13:27.690 --> 00:13:32.460
At the time the nation was
founded, as we all know,

00:13:32.460 --> 00:13:37.590
it was far from anything any of
us would consider a democracy.

00:13:37.590 --> 00:13:45.690
The book begins fittingly, as
