00:14:02.680 --> 00:14:05.840
if it rests on the
consent of the governed.

00:14:05.840 --> 00:14:09.720
And that was a radical
idea then, as well as now.

00:14:09.720 --> 00:14:12.870
And it had a tremendous
force, a tremendous power,

00:14:12.870 --> 00:14:16.620
